summary: Literally just me Classpecting 3 (/kinda 5, actually) BNHA characters because I’m physically able too
title: Literally just me Classpecting 3 (/kinda 5, actually) BNHA characters because I’m physically able too
body:
Izuku Midoriya/Deku - Page of Hope
Do I even need to explain this?
Pages start out with little to none of their aspect (Like how deku had no quirk) and have alot of potential, wich when they realize it, they they can and will probably be the strongest player in the session. 
Note that, his aspect could also be something else, as it could also just be deku ‘roleplaying’ as allmight, who is definitly a hope player.

Katsuki Bakugou - Prince of Heart (With hints of Theif of Rage)
Look, everyone says he’s a rage player, but let’s be honest: This “ Those bound to the aspect of Heart are very concerned with their favorite subject: themselves.“ sounds alot like bakugou, doesn’t it?
Why prince? Cause princes are the Destroyer class.
Some of bakugous actions could be seen as heartless, right? Well let’s remind ourselfs that princes destroy their aspect for themselfs, usually by accident.
And he has obvious theif of rage vibes, wich I’m going to say is probably him acting like his mom (roleplaying as her, basically).
NOTE: I also think twice is a prince (or bard) of heart, but in a different way, Bakugou destroys the aspect of heart for himself in a different way that Jin did. Jin destroyed himself, basically, he destroyed his knowing of if he is himself of if he’s just a clone.

Tenya Iida - Seer(?) of Blood
First off Tenya is definitly trying to roleplay as his brother, but failing at that. I’d say that Tensei is a breath player, and that tenya tries to copy this, however as a blood player, roleplaying as a Breath player could be seen as not too god and even harmful at times.
It’s obvious that he looks up to his brother, and that this has positive effects on him, but honestly, it’s somewhat of a mess decodeing him, cause he tries to be ingenium, a title held by many people, who peobably all have different classpects.
He could also be a mind player.
Just saying.
It fits too.

Tell me if I should do this for other characters aswell.
